main event: A round, white object was seen in the sky over Oil City, Pennsylvania on March 11, 1967. The object would appear and disappear periodically, was very bright, and moved very fast to the northeast.
interesting points: The object was described as round and white in color.
The object would appear and disappear periodically in the sky.
The object was very bright and moved very fast to the northeast.
The witness was a Presburn at Venango General Hospital and was able to clearly see the object.
The witness had never seen anything like this object before.
